<!-- 定義及醫療用途 -->
'''苯海拉明'''（{{lang-en|'''Diphenhydramine'''}}）是一種第一代[[抗組織胺藥|抗組織胺藥]]，主要用於治療[[過敏|過敏症]]<ref name=AHSP2016/>，也可以用於治療[[失眠|失眠]]、[[感冒|感冒]]症狀、[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]震顫和[[噁心|噁心]]、防止[[暈車|暈車]]<ref>{{cite web |author1=Flake ZA, Scalley RD, Bailey AG (March 2004) |title=Practical Selection of Antiemetics |url=https://www.aafp.org/afp/2004/0301/p1169.html |website=American Family Physician |access-date=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2019-04-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420130333/https://www.aafp.org/afp/2004/0301/p1169.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>及[[錐體外症候群|錐體外症候群]]，亦具備[[局部麻醉藥|局部麻醉藥]]的效果<ref name=AHSP2016/>。苯海拉明具有[[鎮靜劑|鎮靜劑]]作用，被部分用於助眠或抗焦慮藥。給藥方式包括口服、[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]及[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]]<ref name=AHSP2016/>。最大效果通常在給藥後約兩小時，效果可持續長達七小時<ref name=AHSP2016>{{cite web|title=Diphenhydramine Hydrochloride|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/diphenhydramine-hydrochloride.html|website=Drugs.com|publisher=American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|accessdate=28 September 2016|date=6 September 2016|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915002404/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/diphenhydramine-hydrochloride.html|archivedate=15 September 2016}}</ref>。<br />

==副作用與機制==
苯海拉明常見的副作用包括[[嗜睡|嗜睡]]、方向感不佳以及[[反胃|反胃]]<ref name=AHSP2016/>，不建議給嬰兒服用<ref name=AHSP2016/>。目前還不清楚在懷孕時使用的風險，不過不建議在[[哺乳|哺乳]]時服用此藥物<ref>{{cite web|title=Diphenhydramine Pregnancy and Breastfeeding Warnings|url=https://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/diphenhydramine.html|website=Drugs.com|accessdate=28 September 2016|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002114958/https://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/diphenhydramine.html|archivedate=2 October 2016}}</ref>。

苯海拉明是第一代的抗阻胺藥，即{{le|H1拮抗劑|H1 antihistamine}}，會阻斷組織胺與H1接受器結合<ref name=AHSP2016/>。與其他H1拮抗劑一樣，正常劑量下亦會導致[[不寧腿綜合症|不寧腿綜合症]]加重<ref>{{cite web |title=Restless Legs Syndrome Fact Sheet |url=https://www.ninds.nih.gov/disorders/patient-caregiver-education/fact-sheets/restless-legs-syndrome-fact-sheet |website=National Institute of Neurological Disorders and Stroke |access-date=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2017-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170728021833/https://www.ninds.nih.gov/Disorders/Patient-Caregiver-Education/Fact-Sheets/Restless-Legs-Syndrome-Fact-Sheet |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

苯海拉明也是[[抗膽鹼劑|抗膽鹼劑]]<ref>{{cite book|last1=Ayd|first1=Frank J.|title=Lexicon of Psychiatry, Neurology, and the Neurosciences|date=2000|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|isbn=978-0-7817-2468-5 | page = 332 | url = https://books.google.ca/books?id=ea_QVG2BFy8C&pg=PA332  | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170908214041/https://books.google.ca/books?id=ea_QVG2BFy8C&pg=PA332 | archive-date = 8 September 2017}}</ref>，會對[[副交感神經|副交感神經]]產生抑制作用，導致[[頭暈|頭暈]]、[[瞳孔放大|瞳孔放大]]、[[心跳過速|心跳過速]]、[[畏光|畏光]]、意識模糊、注意力不集中的副作用。

服用過多的苯海拉明會產生些微心理[[成癮|成癮]]性<ref>{{cite web |author1=Monson K，Schoenstadt A |title=Benadryl Addiction |url=http://allergies.emedtv.com/benadryl/benadryl-addiction.html |website=eMedTV |accessdate=2014-01-04 |archive-date=2014-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104053402/http://allergies.emedtv.com/benadryl/benadryl-addiction.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。<br />雖然擁有[[鎮靜劑|鎮靜劑]]效果，但因每人對藥物適應性不同，機率會產生{{le|異常反應|Paradoxical reaction}}反倒變得活躍<ref>{{cite web |author1=Wendy S.Swanson |title=If It Were My Child: No Benadryl For The Plane |url=https://seattlemamadoc.seattlechildrens.org/if-it-were-my-child-no-benadryl-for-the-plane/ |website=Seattle Children's |accessdate=NOVEMBER 24, 2009 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225070641/https://seattlemamadoc.seattlechildrens.org/if-it-were-my-child-no-benadryl-for-the-plane/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。<br />
苯海拉明與酒精併用會產生{{le|药物相互作用|Interaction}}而加重[[嗜睡|嗜睡]]症狀<ref>{{cite web |title=Diphenhydramine and Alcohol / Food Interactions |url=https://www.drugs.com/food-interactions/diphenhydramine.html |website=Drugs.com |access-date=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2013-02-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130217152320/http://www.drugs.com/food-interactions/diphenhydramine.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==歷史及社會==
苯海拉明最早是由美國化學教授{{le|George Rieveschl|George Rieveschl}}製備，在1946年開始販售<ref>{{cite book|last1=Dörwald|first1=Florencio Zaragoza|title=Lead Optimization for Medicinal Chemists: Pharmacokinetic Properties of Functional Groups and Organic Compounds |date = 2013 | publisher = John Wiley & Sons | isbn = 978-3-527-64565-7 | page = 225 | url = https://books.google.ca/books?id=YTeY9ZEfNccC&pg=PA225 | deadurl = no | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161002085621/https://books.google.ca/books?id=YTeY9ZEfNccC&pg=PA225|archivedate=2 October 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Benadryl|url=http://ohiohistorycentral.org/w/Benadryl?rec=2591|website=Ohio History Central|accessdate=28 September 2016|deadurl=no|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161017192649/http://ohiohistorycentral.org/w/Benadryl?rec=2591|archivedate=17 October 2016}}</ref>。目前是[[通用名药物|通用名药物]]<ref name=AHSP2016/>。在发展中國家的藥價是每劑美金0.01元<ref>{{cite web|title=Diphenhydramine|url=http://mshpriceguide.org/en/single-drug-information/?DMFId=273&searchYear=2014|website=International Drug Price Indicator Guide|accessdate=28 September 2016|archive-date=2020-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927162514/https://mshpriceguide.org/en/single-drug-information/?DMFId=273&searchYear=2014|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在美國，每個月的藥費小於美金25元<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart|title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=978-1-284-05756-0|page=240}}</ref>。苯海拉明的商品名有Benadryl，也有其他的名稱<ref name=AHSP2016/>。在[[尚比亞|尚比亞]]，苯海拉明被禁毒委員會列為管制與禁用藥物<ref>{{cite web |title="List of prohibited and controlled drugs according to chapter 96 of the laws of Zambia" |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131116010729/http://www.gctrips.org/documents/IllegaldrugsinZambia.docx |website=The Drug Enforcement Commission ZAMBIA}}</ref>。

==藥物濫用==
苯海拉明屬於[[通用名药物|通用名药物]]，在大多數國家都可以輕易購買，在某些國家會被作為[[鎮靜劑|鎮靜劑]]或助眠藥物使用。有精神健康問題的人或[[精神分裂症|精神分裂症]]患者為降低因服用典型抗精神病藥物導致的常見副作用[[錐體外症候群|錐體外症候群]]，會使用苯海拉明加以抑制，這使得他們對該藥產生心理[[成癮|成癮]]性。

對於[[青少年|青少年]]而言，苯海拉明帶來的鎮靜作用、[[欣快感|欣快感]]與幻覺為他們帶來精神亢奮與抑制[[憂鬱|憂鬱]]的效果。

2020年5月，在[[抖音|抖音]]上牽起了「苯海拉明挑戰」（{{lang-en|'''Benadryl Challenge'''}}）風潮，鼓勵青少年服用超過十幾片以上的[[抗組胺藥|抗組胺藥]]後，將飄飄欲仙、產生幻覺後的影片發布於TikTok上，導致美國[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]][[沃思堡|沃思堡]]至少三名青少年因而住院。一名青少年服用14片苯海拉明後產生幻覺、說話語無倫次、靜息[[心率|心率]]高達199。2020年8月30日，[[奧克拉荷馬市|奧克拉荷馬市]]當地媒體{{le|WKRG-TV}}報導一名15歲少女因參與此挑戰服藥過量而死亡<ref>{{cite news |author1=Cassandra Sweetman (KFOR) and Nexstar Media Wire |title=Dangerous ‘Benadryl Challenge’ on TikTok blamed for death of Oklahoma teen |url=https://www.wkrg.com/news/dangerous-benadryl-challenge-on-tiktok-blamed-for-death-of-oklahoma-teen/#link=%7B%22role%22:%22standard%22,%22href%22:%22https://www.wkrg.com/news/dangerous-benadryl-challenge-on-tiktok-blamed-for-death-of-oklahoma-teen/%22,%22target%22:%22_blank%22,%22absolute%22:%22%22,%22linkText%22:%22report.%22%7D |work=WKRG-TV |date=2020-08-31 |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211040918/https://www.wkrg.com/news/dangerous-benadryl-challenge-on-tiktok-blamed-for-death-of-oklahoma-teen/#link=%7B%22role%22:%22standard%22,%22href%22:%22https://www.wkrg.com/news/dangerous-benadryl-challenge-on-tiktok-blamed-for-death-of-oklahoma-teen/%22,%22target%22:%22_blank%22,%22absolute%22:%22%22,%22linkText%22:%22report.%22%7D |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這促使[[美國食品藥品監督管理局|美國食品藥品監督管理局]]與Benadryl的製造商[[嬌生公司|嬌生公司]]對藥物濫用行為發出警告：「過量服用Benadryl可能導致嚴重的[[心臟病|心臟病]]、[[癲癇發作|癲癇發作]]、[[昏迷|昏迷]]甚至死亡。」<ref>{{cite news |author1=Dalvin Brown |title='Benadryl Challenge' on TikTok can cause 'serious problems,' the FDA warns |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/money/2020/09/25/tiktoks-benadryl-challenge-can-cause-serious-problems-fda-warns/3528974001/ |work=USA Today |date=2020-09-25 |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118084548/https://www.usatoday.com/story/money/2020/09/25/tiktoks-benadryl-challenge-can-cause-serious-problems-fda-warns/3528974001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>Honeybee Health的首席藥劑師，聯合創始人兼聯合首席CEO Jessica Nouhavandi表示：「Benadryl的{{le|每日最高劑量|maximum daily dose}}為300毫克（mg），每片藥物通常含有25毫克，[[藥物過量|藥物過量]]會導致包括[[嗜睡|嗜睡]]，[[口乾|口乾]]，[[便秘|便秘]]和無法[[排尿|排尿]]的副作用，嚴重時可能導致[[幻覺|幻覺]]、[[精神病|精神病]]、[[癲癇發作|癲癇發作]]或[[昏迷|昏迷]]。」<ref>{{cite news |title=Benadryl Challenge on TikTok Is Dangerous, Experts Say |url=https://www.healthline.com/health-news/benadryl-challenge-on-tiktok-is-dangerous-experts-say#Proper-dosages |work=Healthline |accessdate=2020-09-26 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120223248/https://www.healthline.com/health-news/benadryl-challenge-on-tiktok-is-dangerous-experts-say#Proper-dosages |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

